					"type": 23,
					"value": "Load up CTY_Main_A\r\nopen Recon and set up Roll amazing\r\nGo to -1968; -6; 417\r\nKill S_LOW_BaneiteOfficer09_0c5259f6-3c86-4e84-b61e-42e9f31691ce\r\nClick on the Kill Switch that falls on the ground."
