				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The player has successfully deactivated the 'Motivator' a device that, when triggered, will kill every single Gondian in the foundry (via shock collar) and blow up their families in a far off prison.\r\nThese can trigger the first time you deactivate it (high tension), second time (there's no skill check, but you HAVE to get to it in time), and the third time. "
				}
